name: eternity
description:
Part of a series I shot at the Nordfriedhof in Wiesbaden. This huge cemetery has thousands of graves ranging from the late 19th century to modern times. 

I plan to go back there to shoot some more as it is a very quite and beautiful place.

📍 Wiesbaden, Germany
📸 Konica Autoreflex TC
🔭 Konica Hexanon 50mm f1.7
